{
  "id": "adv_event_2202_01_02",
  "title": "償いの奮闘",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "kkrroom",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、このアイドルの曲は参考になるかも……\n要チェックですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ this idol's song might be a good reference…\nI need to check it out!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.8542176247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "ようし、MVの次はライブ映像を――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ after the music video‚ let's watch the live footage――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.0475508054,
      "endTime": 12.060045178700001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3652.449194599999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "kkrroom",
      "startTime": 12.246711731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、お茶淹れてきたから、一休み\n――って、あ痛ーーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro‚ I brought some tea‚ take a break.\nOops‚ ow!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.246711731,
      "endTime": 17.1853740693,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 120.000000000001
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hit-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3219.9549357000005
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "kkrroom",
      "startTime": 15.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "kkrroom",
      "startTime": 17.3987073263
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "何これ！？\n床、すっごい散らかってるんだけど！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's this!?\nThe floor is incredibly messy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.3987073263,
      "endTime": 21.852040513400002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "愛、これはライブ映像のDVDとかブルーレイだよ\n全部借り物だから、踏んじゃダメだよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ these are live concert DVDs and Blu-rays.\nThey're all borrowed‚ so don't step on them‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.0587070466,
      "endTime": 29.186416721399997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "kkrroom",
      "startTime": 29.3797498067
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "これ、一体何枚あるの！？\n足の踏み場もないよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How many of these are there!?\nThere's no space to walk!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3797498067,
      "endTime": 34.822425683300004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "kkrroom",
      "startTime": 35.0090924263
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "ざっと100枚くらいかなぁ\n雫ちゃんに頼んで貸してもらったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think there are about 100 of them.\nI borrowed them from Shizuku-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.0090924263,
      "endTime": 39.9037860869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "kkrroom",
      "startTime": 40.1104528109
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "これ、全部観るつもりなの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you planning to watch all of them!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.1104528109,
      "endTime": 42.9211103598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "kkrroom",
      "startTime": 43.1277769883
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "それだけじゃないよ。ネットにはまだまだ沢山\n参考になる映像があるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not just that. There are still plenty of videos online\nthat can be a reference.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.1277769883,
      "endTime": 48.5554639656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "インスピレーションがわくまで\nひたすら研究あるのみだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Until inspiration strikes‚\nI'll focus on studying them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.7554638703,
      "endTime": 53.117164691199996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "kkrroom",
      "startTime": 53.3104979197
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "こころは可愛くて才能溢れる逸材なだけじゃなく\nとっても努力家だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro is not just a cute and talented prodigy‚\nshe's also a hard worker.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.3104979197,
      "endTime": 59.2068242709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "kkrroom",
      "startTime": 59.3934909184
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "努力はいいけど、最近こころ全然休んでないでしょ？\nレッスンと食事以外、ずっと部屋にこもってるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Working hard is good‚ but lately‚ Kokoro hasn't been resting at all.\nYou've been cooped up in the room‚ except for lessons and meals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.3934909184,
      "endTime": 68.2801579794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタインイベントには確かに出たいけど\nあんまり根を詰め過ぎるのも良くないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's true that I want to participate in the Valentine's event‚\nbut getting too obsessed isn't good either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4734912555,
      "endTime": 74.7374824206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "kkrroom",
      "startTime": 75.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "大体、こころってチョコ嫌いだよね？\nなんだかいつものこころと違うから私、心配で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ Kokoro doesn't like chocolate‚ right?\nIt feels like Kokoro's acting different than usual‚ so I'm worried…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.0333333333,
      "endTime": 82.8774821919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "kkrroom",
      "startTime": 83.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "愛、何しんみりしてるの？\n賞味期限の切れたラーメンでも食べたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ why do you look so gloomy?\nDid you eat expired ramen or something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0666666667,
      "endTime": 88.64299236939999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "食べてないし、お腹も壊してないよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't eat it‚ and my stomach is fine!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.8333333333,
      "endTime": 92.10133779840001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "kkrroom",
      "startTime": 92.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "……愛の言う通り、チョコは好きじゃないよ\nでも、食べる訳じゃないんだし、関係ないよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…As Ai said‚ I don't like chocolate.\nBut since I'm not eating it‚ it doesn't matter‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.3,
      "endTime": 99.2992504279,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "こころはただ、新曲のセンターを先輩達から奪っちゃう\nいい機会って思っただけなんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just thought it would be a good opportunity\nto snatch the center position for the new song from our senpais.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.6333333333,
      "endTime": 106.8271638711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "kkrroom",
      "startTime": 107.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "はあ！？　何それ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? What's that supposed to mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.0333333333,
      "endTime": 109.46666666670001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "kkrroom",
      "startTime": 109.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～。愛とこころの間にまた格差が出来ちゃうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh~ The gap between Ai and Kokoro is widening again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.6666666667,
      "endTime": 115.6181406657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "調子に乗り過ぎ！\nいつものこころだった！　心配して損したよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't get carried away!\nIt's the usual Kokoro! I worried for nothing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.8333333333,
      "endTime": 121.3932860453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "kkrroom",
      "startTime": 121.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "まぁまぁ。愛も目立てるようにしてあげるから\n……こころの次にだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ alright. I'll make sure you stand out‚ Ai.\n…But after Kokoro‚ of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.6,
      "endTime": 127.6182975847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "kkrroom",
      "startTime": 127.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_02-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことしなくていいよ！　私も手伝う！\nこころだけに任せてたら、新曲が変になっちゃう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have to do that! I'll help too!\nIf we leave it all to Kokoro‚ the new song might turn out weird!",
        "id": ""
      },
